  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../president-obamas-china-trip-final-thoughts">President Obama&#039;s China Trip: Final Thoughts</a></span>
