  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>President Obama departed China today after quite a productive two days.  The major accomplishments on the climate front were the series of agreements signed yesterday.  While expectations for Copenhagen have been somewhat lowered ‚Äì towards a ‚Äúpolitical‚Äù deal rather than completing all the work needed for the full-scale treaty ‚Äì <a href="http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20091118/ap_on_bi_ge/climate
">both Obama and Hu indicated</a> they were working to get to a good deal.</p></div>
